{"tid":1822671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本即將出現大地震？ 3日內2次驚現罕見「地震魚」","createTime":"2020-01-13T05:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T06:05:49.000Z","uid":107755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e782e34bec64bbd43102ab60a380e621b6b61989","tid":1822671,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:52:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/30312/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87-3%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A72%E6%AC%A1%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B-%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%AD%9A/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F30312%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587-3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25A72%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E9%25A9%259A%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%25BD%2595%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E9%25AD%259A%2F1%2F&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=e2a65a41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/30312/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87-3%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A72%E6%AC%A1%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B-%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%AD%9A/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本有「如果看到深海魚，就會發生地震」的傳說，日前日本福井縣就有人發現罕見深海魚皇帶魚（又名皇宮使者）浮現海灘，令民眾十分驚訝。再早前富山縣也發現皇帶魚伏屍沙灘，莫非都是災難前的先兆？<br />\n<br />\n福井縣3日內發現2條皇帶魚出沒事件，其中1條被一對10歲及7歲兄弟發現，出現海灘20分鐘後就游走。另1條為屍體，被一名中學生發現。該皇帶魚約長2.4米，被海浪沖上海灘。正所謂無獨有偶，富山縣同樣有人發現皇帶魚屍體。屍體其後運送到魚津水族館冷凍保藏，現時已作為展品開放給觀眾參觀。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n福井縣越前松島水族館館長鈴木隆史表示，自從2019年7~9月內有5條深海魚被發現後，上一次發現有皇帶魚出沒已是2015年。館長希望如果有人發現，可以儘快聯絡水族館，以作研究用途。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本有傳深海魚出現是地震先兆，這種說法最早出現於1743年的奇談集諸国里人談中。雖然未知真偽。不過去年有大學教授指出深海魚出現就會地震的說法只是迷信，出現時間相信只是巧合"},{"pid":"8f5efbd5746b90b95f462775be8ce2d0391000db","tid":1822671,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"富山睇到立山黑部<br />\n福井其實好靚又靜又小人<br />\n去埋敦賀仲開心<br />\n<br />\n如果日本政府肯比香港後生去呢三個地方<br />\n或者東北幫手補充人口就好"},{"pid":"17188ad24a0ad38fe54646bdc6159958c2b14810","tid":1822671,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"【港共受刑天下制裁大遊行】<br />\n日期｜01 月 19 日（星期日）<br />\n時間｜3.00PM <br />\n地點｜遮打道 至 銅鑼灣SOGO"},{"pid":"e0ff21a184560341d22b94692b830ecdfb9528bb","tid":1822671,"uid":8732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"新年任務！1.19大遊行！和你宵！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822470</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCZ0E6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCZ0E6K.png&h=5d44280a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c38f981d2e631ff8fdbd5cd0ed27f931eef6847","tid":1822671,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:54:08.000Z","msg":"核試<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ebe3128672b3f642ba3eb4617c2f40d4bc3229","tid":1822671,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"日學者發現皇帶魚等深海魚出沒與地震無關 <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190815/s00005/1565866436950/%E6%97%A5%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E7%9A%87%E5%B8%B6%E9%AD%9A%E7%AD%89%E6%B7%B1%E6%B5%B7%E9%AD%9A%E5%87%BA%E6%B2%92%E8%88%87%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E7%84%A1%E9%97%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00005%2F1565866436950%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%259A%2587%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E9%25AD%259A%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AD%259A%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B2%2592%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2597%259C&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGa